51 enum
52 {
53  SAY_JUST_EATEN = -1000175,
54 
55  SPELL_PLACE_CARCASS = 38439,
56  SPELL_JUST_EATEN = 38502,
57  SPELL_NETHER_BREATH = 38467,
58  SPELL_INTANGIBLE_PRESENCE = 36513,
59 
60  QUEST_KINDNESS = 10804,
61  NPC_EVENT_PINGER = 22131,
62 
63  GO_FLAYER_CARCASS = 185155,
64 };

66 struct mob_mature_netherwing_drakeAI : public ScriptedAI
67 {
68  mob_mature_netherwing_drakeAI(Creature* pCreature) : ScriptedAI(pCreature) { Reset(); }
69 
70  ObjectGuid m_playerGuid;
71 
72  uint32 m_uiEatTimer;
73  uint32 m_uiCreditTimer;
74  uint32 m_uiNetherbreathTimer;
75  uint32 m_uiIntangiblePresenceTimer;
76 
77  void Reset() override
78  {
79  m_playerGuid.Clear();
80 
81  m_uiEatTimer = 0;
82  m_uiCreditTimer = 0;
83  m_uiNetherbreathTimer = 5000;
84  m_uiIntangiblePresenceTimer = 12000;
85  }
86 
87  void SpellHit(Unit* pCaster, SpellEntry const* pSpell) override
88  {
89  if (m_uiEatTimer || m_uiCreditTimer)
90  return;
91 
92  if (pCaster->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER && pSpell->Id == SPELL_PLACE_CARCASS && !m_creature->HasAura(SPELL_JUST_EATEN))
93  {
94  m_playerGuid = pCaster->GetObjectGuid();
95  m_uiEatTimer = 5000;
96  }
97  }
98 
99  void MovementInform(uint32 uiMoveType, uint32 uiPointId) override
100  {
101  if (uiMoveType != POINT_MOTION_TYPE)
102  return;
103 
104  if (uiPointId)
105  {
106  m_uiCreditTimer = 7000;
107  m_creature->SetLevitate(false);
108  m_creature->HandleEmote(EMOTE_ONESHOT_ATTACKUNARMED);
109  m_creature->RemoveByteFlag(UNIT_FIELD_BYTES_1, UNIT_BYTES_1_OFFSET_MISC_FLAGS, UNIT_BYTE1_FLAG_FLY_ANIM);
110  }
111  }
112 
113  void JustReachedHome() override
114  {
115  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->Clear();
116  }
117 
118  void UpdateAI(const uint32 uiDiff) override
119  {
120  if (m_uiEatTimer)
121  {
122  if (m_uiEatTimer <= uiDiff)
123  {
124  if (GameObject* pGo = GetClosestGameObjectWithEntry(m_creature, GO_FLAYER_CARCASS, 80.0f))
125  {
126  if (m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->GetCurrentMovementGeneratorType() == WAYPOINT_MOTION_TYPE)
127  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->MovementExpired();
128 
129  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->MoveIdle();
130 
131  float fX, fY, fZ;
132  pGo->GetContactPoint(m_creature, fX, fY, fZ, CONTACT_DISTANCE);
133 
134  m_creature->SetWalk(false);
135  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(1, fX, fY, fZ);
136  }
137  m_uiEatTimer = 0;
138  }
139  else
140  m_uiEatTimer -= uiDiff;
141 
142  return;
143  }
144  if (m_uiCreditTimer)
145  {
146  if (m_uiCreditTimer <= uiDiff)
147  {
148  DoCastSpellIfCan(m_creature, SPELL_JUST_EATEN);
149  DoScriptText(SAY_JUST_EATEN, m_creature);
150 
151  if (Player* pPlayer = m_creature->GetMap()->GetPlayer(m_playerGuid))
152  pPlayer->KilledMonsterCredit(NPC_EVENT_PINGER, m_creature->GetObjectGuid());
153 
154  Reset();
155  m_creature->SetLevitate(true);
156  m_creature->SetByteFlag(UNIT_FIELD_BYTES_1, UNIT_BYTES_1_OFFSET_MISC_FLAGS, UNIT_BYTE1_FLAG_FLY_ANIM);
157  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->Clear();
158  m_uiCreditTimer = 0;
159  }
160  else
161  m_uiCreditTimer -= uiDiff;
162 
163  return;
164  }
165 
166  if (!m_creature->SelectHostileTarget() || !m_creature->GetVictim())
167  return;
168 
169  if (m_uiNetherbreathTimer < uiDiff)
170  {
171  DoCastSpellIfCan(m_creature->GetVictim(), SPELL_NETHER_BREATH);
172  m_uiNetherbreathTimer = urand(9000, 13000);
173  }
174  else
175  m_uiNetherbreathTimer -= uiDiff;
176 
177  if (m_uiIntangiblePresenceTimer < uiDiff)
178  {
179  DoCastSpellIfCan(m_creature->GetVictim(), SPELL_INTANGIBLE_PRESENCE);
180  m_uiIntangiblePresenceTimer = urand(12000, 16000);
181  }
182  else
183  m_uiIntangiblePresenceTimer -= uiDiff;
184 
185  DoMeleeAttackIfReady();
186  }
187 };
188 
189 UnitAI* GetAI_mob_mature_netherwing_drake(Creature* pCreature)
190 {
191  return new mob_mature_netherwing_drakeAI(pCreature);
192 }

201

203  SPELL_FORCE_OF_NELTHARAKU = 38775,
204 
205  EMOTE_ON_HIT_FORCE = -1015001,
206

208  NPC_DRAGONMAW_SUBJUGATOR = 21718,

212 struct mob_enslaved_netherwing_drakeAI : public ScriptedAI
213 {
214  mob_enslaved_netherwing_drakeAI(Creature* creature) : ScriptedAI(creature), m_uiFlyTimer(0), m_disabled(false)
215  {
216  Reset();
217  }
218 
219  ObjectGuid m_playerGuid;
220  uint32 m_uiFlyTimer;
221  bool m_disabled;
222 
223  void Reset() override
224  {
225  m_creature->SetCanFly(false);
226  m_creature->SetHover(false);
227  }
228 
229  void JustRespawned() override
230  {
231  ScriptedAI::JustRespawned();
232  m_disabled = false;
233  }
234 
235  void SpellHit(Unit* pCaster, const SpellEntry* pSpell) override
236  {
237  if (pSpell->Id == SPELL_HIT_FORCE_OF_NELTHARAKU && !m_disabled)
238  {
239  if (Player* pPlayer = pCaster->GetBeneficiaryPlayer())
240  {
241  m_uiFlyTimer = 2500;
242  m_disabled = true;
243  m_playerGuid = pPlayer->GetObjectGuid();
244 
245  DoScriptText(EMOTE_ON_HIT_FORCE, m_creature);
246 
247  m_creature->SetFactionTemporary(FACTION_FRIENDLY, TEMPFACTION_RESTORE_RESPAWN);
248 
249  if (Creature* pDragonmaw = GetClosestCreatureWithEntry(m_creature, NPC_DRAGONMAW_SUBJUGATOR, 20.0f))
250  AttackStart(pDragonmaw);
251  }
252  }
253  }
254 
255  void MovementInform(uint32 uiMoveType, uint32 uiPointId) override
256  {
257  if (uiMoveType != POINT_MOTION_TYPE)
258  return;
259 
260  if (uiPointId)
261  m_creature->ForcedDespawn();
262  }
263 
264  void UpdateAI(const uint32 uiDiff) override
265  {
266  if (!m_creature->SelectHostileTarget() || !m_creature->GetVictim())
267  {
268  if (m_uiFlyTimer)
269  {
270  if (m_uiFlyTimer <= uiDiff)
271  {
272  if (Player* pPlayer = m_creature->GetMap()->GetPlayer(m_playerGuid))
273  {
274  DoCastSpellIfCan(pPlayer, SPELL_FORCE_OF_NELTHARAKU, CAST_TRIGGERED);
275  m_playerGuid.Clear();
276 
277  float fX, fY, fZ;
278 
279  // Get an escape position
280  if (Creature* pEscapeDummy = GetClosestCreatureWithEntry(m_creature, NPC_ESCAPE_DUMMY, 50.0f))
281  pEscapeDummy->GetPosition(fX, fY, fZ);
282  else
283  {
284  m_creature->GetRandomPoint(m_creature->GetPositionX(), m_creature->GetPositionY(), m_creature->GetPositionZ(), 20.0f, fX, fY, fZ);
285  fZ += 25;
286  }
287  m_creature->SetCanFly(true);
288  m_creature->SetHover(true);
289  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(1, fX, fY, fZ);
290  }
291  m_uiFlyTimer = 0;
292  }
293  else
294  m_uiFlyTimer -= uiDiff;
295  }
296 
297  return;
298  }
299 
300  DoMeleeAttackIfReady();
301  }
302 };

319  SAY_PEON_5 = -1000656,
320 
321  SPELL_SERVING_MUTTON = 40468,
322  NPC_DRAGONMAW_KILL_CREDIT = 23209,
323  EQUIP_ID_MUTTON = 2202,

327 struct npc_dragonmaw_peonAI : public ScriptedAI
328 {
329  npc_dragonmaw_peonAI(Creature* pCreature) : ScriptedAI(pCreature) { Reset(); }
330 
331  ObjectGuid m_playerGuid;
332  uint32 m_uiPoisonTimer;
333  uint32 m_uiMoveTimer;
334  uint32 m_uiEatTimer;
335 
336  void Reset() override
337  {
338  m_playerGuid.Clear();
339  m_uiPoisonTimer = 0;
340  m_uiMoveTimer = 0;
341  m_uiEatTimer = 0;
342 
343  SetEquipmentSlots(true);
344  }
345 
346  bool SetPlayerTarget(ObjectGuid playerGuid)
347  {
348  // Check if event already started
349  if (m_playerGuid)
350  return false;
351 
352  m_playerGuid = playerGuid;
353  m_uiMoveTimer = 500;
354  return true;
355  }
356 
357  void MovementInform(uint32 uiType, uint32 uiPointId) override
358  {
359  if (uiType != POINT_MOTION_TYPE)
360  return;
361 
362  if (uiPointId == POINT_DEST)
363  {
364  m_uiEatTimer = 2000;
365  m_uiPoisonTimer = 3000;
366 
367  switch (urand(0, 4))
368  {
369  case 0: DoScriptText(SAY_PEON_1, m_creature); break;
370  case 1: DoScriptText(SAY_PEON_2, m_creature); break;
371  case 2: DoScriptText(SAY_PEON_3, m_creature); break;
372  case 3: DoScriptText(SAY_PEON_4, m_creature); break;
373  case 4: DoScriptText(SAY_PEON_5, m_creature); break;
374  }
375  }
376  }
377 
378  void UpdateAI(const uint32 uiDiff) override
379  {
380  if (m_uiMoveTimer)
381  {
382  if (m_uiMoveTimer <= uiDiff)
383  {
384  if (Player* pPlayer = m_creature->GetMap()->GetPlayer(m_playerGuid))
385  {
386  GameObject* pMutton = pPlayer->GetGameObject(SPELL_SERVING_MUTTON);
387 
388  // Workaround for broken function GetGameObject
389  if (!pMutton)
390  {
391  const SpellEntry* pSpell = GetSpellStore()->LookupEntry<SpellEntry>(SPELL_SERVING_MUTTON);
392 
393  uint32 uiGameobjectEntry = pSpell->EffectMiscValue[EFFECT_INDEX_0];
394 
395  // this can fail, but very low chance
396  pMutton = GetClosestGameObjectWithEntry(pPlayer, uiGameobjectEntry, 2 * INTERACTION_DISTANCE);
397  }
398 
399  if (pMutton)
400  {
401  float fX, fY, fZ;
402  pMutton->GetContactPoint(m_creature, fX, fY, fZ, CONTACT_DISTANCE);
403 
404  m_creature->SetWalk(false);
405  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(POINT_DEST, fX, fY, fZ);
406  }
407  }
408 
409  m_uiMoveTimer = 0;
410  }
411  else
412  m_uiMoveTimer -= uiDiff;
413  }
414  else if (m_uiEatTimer)
415  {
416  if (m_uiEatTimer <= uiDiff)
417  {
418  SetEquipmentSlots(false, EQUIP_ID_MUTTON, EQUIP_UNEQUIP);
419  m_creature->HandleEmote(EMOTE_ONESHOT_EAT_NOSHEATHE);
420  m_uiEatTimer = 0;
421  }
422  else
423  m_uiEatTimer -= uiDiff;
424  }
425  else if (m_uiPoisonTimer)
426  {
427  if (m_uiPoisonTimer <= uiDiff)
428  {
429  if (Player* pPlayer = m_creature->GetMap()->GetPlayer(m_playerGuid))
430  pPlayer->KilledMonsterCredit(NPC_DRAGONMAW_KILL_CREDIT, m_creature->GetObjectGuid());
431 
432  m_uiPoisonTimer = 0;
433 
434  // dies
435  m_creature->SetDeathState(JUST_DIED);
436  m_creature->SetHealth(0);
437  }
438  else
439  m_uiPoisonTimer -= uiDiff;
440  }
441 
442  if (!m_creature->SelectHostileTarget())
443  return;
444 
445  DoMeleeAttackIfReady();
446  }
447 };
448 
449 bool EffectDummyCreature_npc_dragonmaw_peon(Unit* pCaster, uint32 uiSpellId, SpellEffectIndex uiEffIndex, Creature* pCreatureTarget, ObjectGuid /*originalCasterGuid*/)
450 {
451  if (uiEffIndex != EFFECT_INDEX_1 || uiSpellId != SPELL_SERVING_MUTTON || pCaster->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
452  return false;
453 
454  npc_dragonmaw_peonAI* pPeonAI = dynamic_cast<npc_dragonmaw_peonAI*>(pCreatureTarget->AI());
455 
456  if (!pPeonAI)
457  return false;
458 
459  if (pPeonAI->SetPlayerTarget(pCaster->GetObjectGuid()))
460  {
461  pCreatureTarget->HandleEmote(EMOTE_ONESHOT_NONE);
462  return true;
463  }
464 
465  return false;
466 }

499 struct npc_wildaAI : public npc_escortAI
500 {
501  npc_wildaAI(Creature* pCreature) : npc_escortAI(pCreature)
502  {
503  // the creature is floating in a prison; no quest available first;
504  // the floating prison setup and quest flag restore is handled by DB
505  m_creature->SetLevitate(true);
506  m_creature->RemoveFlag(UNIT_NPC_FLAGS, UNIT_NPC_FLAG_QUESTGIVER);
507 
508  Reset();
509  }
510

515  void Reset() override
516  {
517  m_uiHealingTimer = 0;
518  m_uiShockTimer = 1000;

523 
524  void Aggro(Unit* /*pWho*/) override
525  {
526  if (roll_chance_i(30))
527  DoCastSpellIfCan(m_creature, SPELL_EARTHBING_TOTEM);

529 
530  void WaypointReached(uint32 uiPointId) override
531  {
532  switch (uiPointId)
533  {
534  case 9:
535  case 27:
536  case 31:
537  case 33:
538  case 40:
539  case 44:
540  case 52:
541  DoSpawnAssassin();
542  break;
543  case 14:
544  if (Player* pPlayer = GetPlayerForEscort())
545  DoScriptText(SAY_WIL_FREE_SPIRITS, m_creature, pPlayer);
546  DoCastSpellIfCan(m_creature, SPELL_BREAK_WATER_PRISON);
547  break;
548  case 15:
549  if (Player* pPlayer = GetPlayerForEscort())
550  DoScriptText(SAY_WIL_FIND_EXIT, m_creature, pPlayer);
551  DoFreeSpirits();
552  break;
553  case 16:
554  DoSpawnAssassin(2);
555  break;
556  case 41:
557  if (Player* pPlayer = GetPlayerForEscort())
558  DoScriptText(SAY_WIL_JUST_AHEAD, m_creature, pPlayer);
559  break;
560  case 53:
561  if (Player* pPlayer = GetPlayerForEscort())
562  {
563  DoDespawnSpirits();
564  m_creature->SetFacingToObject(pPlayer);
565  DoScriptText(SAY_WIL_END, m_creature, pPlayer);
566  pPlayer->RewardPlayerAndGroupAtEventExplored(QUEST_ESCAPE_COILSCAR, m_creature);
567  }
568  break;
569  }
570  }
571 
572  void JustSummoned(Creature* pSummoned) override
573  {
574  if (pSummoned->GetEntry() == NPC_COILSKAR_ASSASSIN)
575  {
576  if (Player* pPlayer = GetPlayerForEscort())
577  pSummoned->AI()->AttackStart(pPlayer);
578  }
579  }
580 
581  // wrapper to spawn assassin and do text
582  void DoSpawnAssassin(uint8 uiCount = 1)
583  {
584  // unknown where they actually appear
585  float fX, fY, fZ;
586  for (uint8 i = 0; i < uiCount; ++i)
587  {
588  m_creature->GetRandomPoint(m_creature->GetPositionX(), m_creature->GetPositionY(), m_creature->GetPositionZ(), 10.0f, fX, fY, fZ);
589  m_creature->SummonCreature(NPC_COILSKAR_ASSASSIN, fX, fY, fZ, 0.0f, TEMPSPAWN_TIMED_OOC_OR_DEAD_DESPAWN, 10000);
590  }
591 
592  // random chance to yell
593  if (roll_chance_i(20))
594  return;
595 
596  // random text when assassin is summoned
597  switch (urand(0, 6))
598  {
599  case 0: DoScriptText(SAY_WIL_PROGRESS_1, m_creature); break;
600  case 1: DoScriptText(SAY_WIL_PROGRESS_2, m_creature); break;
601  case 2: DoScriptText(SAY_WIL_PROGRESS_3, m_creature); break;
602  case 3: DoScriptText(SAY_WIL_PROGRESS_4, m_creature); break;
603  case 4: DoScriptText(SAY_WIL_PROGRESS_5, m_creature); break;
604  case 5: DoScriptText(SAY_WIL_AGGRO_1, m_creature); break;
605  case 6: DoScriptText(SAY_WIL_AGGRO_2, m_creature); break;
606  }
607  }
608 
609  // free the water spirits
610  void DoFreeSpirits()
611  {
612  CreatureList lSpiritsInRange;
613  GetCreatureListWithEntryInGrid(lSpiritsInRange, m_creature, NPC_CAPTURED_WATER_SPIRIT, 50.0f);
614 
615  if (lSpiritsInRange.empty())
616  return;
617 
618  // all spirits follow
619  for (Creature* spirit : lSpiritsInRange)
620  {
621  spirit->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(SPELL_WATER_BUBBLE);
622  spirit->StopMoving();
623  spirit->GetMotionMaster()->MoveFollow(m_creature, m_creature->GetDistance(spirit) * 0.25f, M_PI_F / 2 + m_creature->GetAngle(spirit), true);
624  spirit->SetFactionTemporary(FACTION_ESCORT_N_FRIEND_ACTIVE, TEMPFACTION_RESTORE_RESPAWN);
625  spirit->SetLevitate(false);
626  }
627  }
628 
629  void DoDespawnSpirits()
630  {
631  CreatureList lSpiritsInRange;
632  GetCreatureListWithEntryInGrid(lSpiritsInRange, m_creature, NPC_CAPTURED_WATER_SPIRIT, 50.0f);
633 
634  if (lSpiritsInRange.empty())
635  return;
636 
637  // all spirits follow
638  for (CreatureList::const_iterator itr = lSpiritsInRange.begin(); itr != lSpiritsInRange.end(); ++itr)
639  {
640  (*itr)->ForcedDespawn(6000);
641  (*itr)->SetLevitate(true);
642  }
643  }
644 
645  void UpdateEscortAI(const uint32 uiDiff) override
646  {
647  if (!m_creature->SelectHostileTarget() || !m_creature->GetVictim())
648  return;
649 
650  if (m_uiLightningTimer < uiDiff)
651  {
652  if (DoCastSpellIfCan(m_creature->GetVictim(), SPELL_CHAIN_LIGHTNING) == CAST_OK)
653  m_uiLightningTimer = 4000;
654  }
655  else
656  m_uiLightningTimer -= uiDiff;
657 
658  if (m_uiShockTimer < uiDiff)
659  {
660  if (DoCastSpellIfCan(m_creature->GetVictim(), SPELL_FROST_SHOCK) == CAST_OK)
661  m_uiShockTimer = 10000;
662  }
663  else
664  m_uiShockTimer -= uiDiff;
665 
666  if (m_creature->GetHealthPercent() <= 30.0f)
667  {
668  if (m_uiHealingTimer < uiDiff)
669  {
670  DoCastSpellIfCan(m_creature, SPELL_HEALING_WAVE);
671  m_uiHealingTimer = 15000;
672  }
673  else
674  m_uiHealingTimer -= uiDiff;
675  }
676 
677  DoMeleeAttackIfReady();
678  }
679 };
680 
681 UnitAI* GetAI_npc_wilda(Creature* pCreature)
682 {
683  return new npc_wildaAI(pCreature);
684 }

695  pEscortAI->Start(false, pPlayer, pQuest);
696  }
697  return true;
698 }

833 struct mob_torlothAI : public CombatAI
834 {
835  mob_torlothAI(Creature* creature) : CombatAI(creature, TORLOTH_ACTION_MAX)
836  {

838  AddCombatAction(TORLOTH_SHADOWFURY, 18000u);
839  AddCombatAction(TORLOTH_SPELL_REFLECTION, 25000u);
840  AddCustomAction(TORLOTH_ANIMATIONS, 4000u, [&]() {HandleAnimation(); });
841  }
842 
843  ObjectGuid m_lordIllidanGuid;
844  ObjectGuid m_playerGuid;
845 
846  uint8 m_uiAnimationCount;
847 
848  void Reset() override
849  {
850  CombatAI::Reset();
851  m_lordIllidanGuid.Clear();
852  m_playerGuid.Clear();
853 
854  m_uiAnimationCount = 0;
855 
856  // make him not attackable for the time of animation
857  SetCombatMovement(false);

859 
860  void FailEvent()
861  {
862  m_creature->ForcedDespawn();
863  if (Unit* spawner = m_creature->GetSpawner()) // get controller of event
864  SendAIEvent(AI_EVENT_CUSTOM_A, m_creature, spawner); // fail
865  }
866 
867  void JustRespawned() override
868  {
869  CombatAI::JustRespawned();
870  DoCastSpellIfCan(nullptr, SPELL_SPIRIT_PARTICLES, CAST_TRIGGERED | CAST_AURA_NOT_PRESENT);
871  DoCastSpellIfCan(nullptr, SPELL_SHADOWFORM, CAST_TRIGGERED | CAST_AURA_NOT_PRESENT);
872  }
873 
874  void EnterEvadeMode() override
875  {
876  CombatAI::EnterEvadeMode(); // cleanup
877  FailEvent();
878  }
879 
880  void HandleAnimation()
881  {
882  Creature* creature = m_creature;
883 
884  if (TorlothAnim[m_uiAnimationCount].uiCreature == LORD_ILLIDAN)
885  {
886  creature = m_creature->GetMap()->GetCreature(m_lordIllidanGuid);
887 
888  if (!creature)
889  {
890  m_creature->ForcedDespawn();
891  return;
892  }
893  }
894 
895  if (TorlothAnim[m_uiAnimationCount].iTextId)
896  DoScriptText(TorlothAnim[m_uiAnimationCount].iTextId, creature);
897 
898  switch (m_uiAnimationCount)
899  {
900  case 0:
901  m_creature->SetStandState(UNIT_STAND_STATE_KNEEL);
902  break;
903  case 3:
904  m_creature->SetStandState(UNIT_STAND_STATE_STAND);
905  if (Player* target = m_creature->GetMap()->GetPlayer(m_playerGuid))
906  m_creature->SetFacingToObject(target);
907  break;
908  case 5:
909  {
910  SetCombatMovement(true);
911  m_creature->setFaction(FACTION_HOSTILE);
912  m_creature->RemoveFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_IMMUNE_TO_PLAYER);
913  if (Player* target = m_creature->GetMap()->GetPlayer(m_playerGuid))
914  AttackStart(target);
915  else
916  FailEvent();
917  break;
918  }
919  }
920 
921  if (uint32 timer = TorlothAnim[m_uiAnimationCount].uiTimer)
922  ResetTimer(TORLOTH_ANIMATIONS, timer);
923  ++m_uiAnimationCount;
924  }
925 
926  void JustDied(Unit* /*killer*/) override
927  {
928  if (Player* player = m_creature->GetMap()->GetPlayer(m_playerGuid))
929  {
930  player->RewardPlayerAndGroupAtEventExplored(QUEST_BATTLE_OF_THE_CRIMSON_WATCH, m_creature);
931 
932  if (Creature* lordIllidan = m_creature->GetMap()->GetCreature(m_lordIllidanGuid))
933  {
934  DoScriptText(SAY_EVENT_COMPLETED, lordIllidan, player);
935  lordIllidan->AI()->EnterEvadeMode();
936  }
937  }
938  if (Unit* spawner = m_creature->GetSpawner()) // get controller of event
939  SendAIEvent(AI_EVENT_CUSTOM_B, m_creature, spawner); // success
940  }
941 
942  void ExecuteAction(uint32 action) override
943  {
944  switch (action)
945  {
946  case TORLOTH_CLEAVE:
947  if (DoCastSpellIfCan(m_creature->GetVictim(), SPELL_CLEAVE) == CAST_OK)
948  ResetCombatAction(action, 15000);
949  break;
950  case TORLOTH_SHADOWFURY:
951  if (DoCastSpellIfCan(m_creature->GetVictim(), SPELL_SHADOWFURY) == CAST_OK)
952  ResetCombatAction(action, 20000);
953  break;
954  case TORLOTH_SPELL_REFLECTION:
955  if (DoCastSpellIfCan(nullptr, SPELL_SPELL_REFLECTION) == CAST_OK)
956  ResetCombatAction(action, 30000);
957  break;
958  }
959  }
960 };

970  GuidVector m_spawns;

1002  if (Creature* marcus = GetClosestCreatureWithEntry(m_creature, NPC_MARCUS_AURALION, 20.f))

1012  void ReceiveAIEvent(AIEventType eventType, Unit* /*sender*/, Unit* /*invoker*/, uint32 /*miscValue*/) override
1013  {
1014  if (eventType == AI_EVENT_CUSTOM_A) // failed - sent by torloth
1015  FailEvent();
1016  else if (eventType == AI_EVENT_CUSTOM_B) // success
1017  Reset();

1019 
1020  void SummonWave()
1021  {
1022  uint8 uiCount = WavesInfo[m_uiWaveCount].uiSpawnCount;
1023  uint8 uiLocIndex = WavesInfo[m_uiWaveCount].uiUsedSpawnPoint;
1024  uint8 uiFelguardCount = 0;
1025  uint8 uiDreadlordCount = 0;
1026 
1027  for (uint8 i = 0; i < uiCount; ++i)
1028  {
1029  float fLocX = SpawnLocation[uiLocIndex + i].fLocX;
1030  float fLocY = SpawnLocation[uiLocIndex + i].fLocY;
1031  float fLocZ = SpawnLocation[uiLocIndex + i].fLocZ;
1032  float fOrient = SpawnLocation[uiLocIndex + i].fOrient;
1033 
1034  if (Creature* pSpawn = m_creature->SummonCreature(WavesInfo[m_uiWaveCount].uiCreatureId, fLocX, fLocY, fLocZ, fOrient, TEMPSPAWN_TIMED_OOC_OR_DEAD_DESPAWN, 30000))
1035  {
1036  if (m_uiWaveCount) // only in first wave
1037  continue;
1038 
1039  if (!urand(0, 2) && uiFelguardCount < 2)
1040  {
1041  pSpawn->SetDisplayId(MODEL_ID_FELGUARD);
1042  ++uiFelguardCount;
1043  }
1044  else if (uiDreadlordCount < 3)
1045  {
1046  pSpawn->SetDisplayId(MODEL_ID_DREADLORD);
1047  ++uiDreadlordCount;
1048  }
1049  else if (uiFelguardCount < 2)
1050  {
1051  pSpawn->SetDisplayId(MODEL_ID_FELGUARD);
1052  ++uiFelguardCount;
1053  }
1054  }
1055  }
1056 
1057  ++m_uiWaveCount;
1058  m_uiWaveTimer = WavesInfo[m_uiWaveCount].uiSpawnTimer;
1059  m_uiAnnounceTimer = WavesInfo[m_uiWaveCount].uiYellTimer;
1060  }
1061 
1062  void JustSummoned(Creature* summoned) override
1063  {
1064  // increment mob count
1065  ++m_uiMobCount;
1066 
1067  if (!m_playerGuid)
1068  return;
1069 
1070  if (summoned->GetEntry() == NPC_TORLOTH_THE_MAGNIFICENT)
1071  {
1072  if (mob_torlothAI* pTorlothAI = dynamic_cast<mob_torlothAI*>(summoned->AI()))
1073  {
1074  pTorlothAI->m_lordIllidanGuid = m_creature->GetObjectGuid();
1075  pTorlothAI->m_playerGuid = m_playerGuid;
1076  }
1077  }
1078  else
1079  {
1080  if (Player* target = m_creature->GetMap()->GetPlayer(m_playerGuid))
1081  summoned->AI()->AttackStart(target);
1082  }
1083  }
1084 
1085  void SummonedCreatureJustDied(Creature* creature) override
1086  {
1087  if (creature->GetEntry() != NPC_TORLOTH_THE_MAGNIFICENT)
1088  {
1089  // decrement mob count
1090  --m_uiMobCount;
1091 
1092  if (!m_uiMobCount)
1093  m_bWaveAnnounced = false;
1094  }
1095  }
1096 
1097  void CheckEventFail()
1098  {
1099  Player* player = m_creature->GetMap()->GetPlayer(m_playerGuid);
1100 
1101  if (!player)
1102  return;
1103 
1104  if (!player->CheckForGroup([&](Player const* player) -> bool
1105  {
1106  if (!player->IsAlive())
1107  return false;
1108 
1109  if (player->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_BATTLE_OF_THE_CRIMSON_WATCH) != QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE)
1110  return false;
1111 
1112  if (!player->IsWithinDistInMap(m_creature, EVENT_AREA_RADIUS))
1113  return false;
1114 
1115  return true;
1116  }))
1117  {
1118  player->FailQuestForGroup(QUEST_BATTLE_OF_THE_CRIMSON_WATCH);
1119  FailEvent();
1120  }
1121  }
1122 
1123  void UpdateAI(const uint32 uiDiff) override
1124  {
1125  if (!m_playerGuid || !m_bEventStarted)
1126  return;
1127 
1128  if (!m_uiMobCount && m_uiWaveCount < 4)
1129  {
1130  if (!m_bWaveAnnounced && m_uiAnnounceTimer < uiDiff)
1131  {
1132  DoScriptText(WavesInfo[m_uiWaveCount].iTextId, m_creature);
1133  m_bWaveAnnounced = true;
1134  }
1135  else
1136  m_uiAnnounceTimer -= uiDiff;
1137 
1138  if (m_uiWaveTimer < uiDiff)
1139  SummonWave();
1140  else
1141  m_uiWaveTimer -= uiDiff;
1142  }
1143 
1144  if (m_uiCheckTimer < uiDiff)
1145  {
1146  CheckEventFail();
1147  m_uiCheckTimer = 2000;
1148  }
1149  else
1150  m_uiCheckTimer -= uiDiff;
1151  }
1152 };

1161  if (npc_lord_illidan_stormrageAI* illidanAI = dynamic_cast<npc_lord_illidan_stormrageAI*>(lordIllidan->AI()))
1162  if (!illidanAI->m_bEventStarted)
1163  illidanAI->StartEvent(player);
1164 
1165  return true;
1166 }

1255  void UpdateAI(const uint32 diff) override
1256  {
1257  if (m_uiElementalSieveTimer <= diff)
1258  {

1261  }
1262  else

1264  }
1265 };

1300 {

1513  void MovementInform(uint32 motionType, uint32 pointId) override
1514  {
1515  if (motionType != POINT_MOTION_TYPE)
1516  return;
1517 
1518  switch (pointId)
1519  {
1520  case 0:
1521  case 1:
1522  case 2:
1523  case 3:
1524  case 4:
1525  case 5:
1526  case 6:
1527  case 7:
1528  case 8:
1529  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(pointId + 1, DeathwailDescentCoords[pointId + 1].xCoord, DeathwailDescentCoords[pointId + 1].yCoord, DeathwailDescentCoords[pointId + 1].zCoord);
1530  break;
1531  case 9:
1532  DoScriptText(SAY_HEART_RETRIEVED, m_creature);
1533  SetReactState(REACT_AGGRESSIVE);
1534  m_creature->RemoveByteFlag(UNIT_FIELD_BYTES_1, UNIT_BYTES_1_OFFSET_MISC_FLAGS, UNIT_BYTE1_FLAG_FLY_ANIM);
1535  m_creature->SetLevitate(false);
1536 
1537  if (GameObject* goHoF = GetClosestGameObjectWithEntry(m_creature, GOBJECT_HEART_OF_FURY, 30.0f))
1538  {
1539  goHoF->SetRespawnTime(5 * MINUTE);
1540  goHoF->Refresh();
1541  }
1542  if (!m_cHOFVisualTrigger)
1543  m_cHOFVisualTrigger = GetClosestCreatureWithEntry(m_creature, NPC_HOF_VISUAL_TRIGGER, 175.0f);
1544  if (m_cHOFVisualTrigger)
1545  m_cHOFVisualTrigger->ForcedDespawn();
1546 
1547  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->Clear(false, true);
1548  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->MoveIdle();
1549  break;
1550  }
1551  }
1552 
1553  // true = event started normally
1554  // false = something's wrong, ignore
1555  bool SoulstealerEnteredCombat(Creature* /*unit*/, Unit* attacker)
1556  {
1557  if (!m_bEventInProgress)
1558  {
1559  // Begin event
1560  m_bEventInProgress = true;
1561  m_creature->SetActiveObjectState(true);
1562 
1563  m_cHOFVisualTrigger = GetClosestCreatureWithEntry(m_creature, NPC_HOF_VISUAL_TRIGGER, 175.0f);
1564  m_cDeathwailTrigger = GetClosestCreatureWithEntry(m_creature, NPC_DEATHWAIL_VISUAL_TRIG, 175.0f);
1565 
1566  CreatureList lOtherChannelers;
1567  GetCreatureListWithEntryInGrid(lOtherChannelers, m_creature, NPC_SHADOWMOON_SOULSTEALER, 175.0f);
1568 
1569  for (auto& lOtherChanneler : lOtherChannelers)
1570  if (lOtherChanneler->IsAlive())
1571  {
1572  lOtherChanneler->AI()->AttackStart(attacker);
1573  lOtherChanneler->SetActiveObjectState(true);
1574 
1575  // agro on party members
1576  if (Player* player = m_creature->GetMap()->GetPlayer(attacker->GetObjectGuid()))
1577  if (Group* group = player->GetGroup())
1578  for (GroupReference* ref = group->GetFirstMember(); ref != nullptr; ref = ref->next())
1579  {
1580  Player* member = ref->getSource();
1581  if (member && member->IsAlive() && m_cHOFVisualTrigger && m_cHOFVisualTrigger->IsWithinDistInMap(member, MAX_PLAYER_DISTANCE))
1582  lOtherChanneler->AI()->AttackStart(member);
1583  }
1584 
1585  m_lSoulstealers.push_back(lOtherChanneler);
1586  }
1587 
1588  m_playerGuid = attacker->GetObjectGuid();
1589  DoSummonWave();
1590  }
1591  else if (m_bDeathwailGrounded)
1592  return false; // possbile edge case
1593 
1594  return true;
1595  }
1596 
1597  void SoulstealerDied(Creature* unit)
1598  {
1599  m_lSoulstealers.remove(unit);
1600 
1601  if (m_bEventInProgress && !m_bDeathwailGrounded && m_lSoulstealers.empty())
1602  DoBeginDescent();
1603  }

1612  void SpellHitTarget(Unit* pTarget, SpellEntry const* pSpellEntry) override
1613  {
1614  if (pSpellEntry->Id == SPELL_FEL_FIREBALL && pTarget->GetEntry() == NPC_DEATHWAIL_VISUAL_TRIG)
1615  if (Creature* summoner = GetClosestCreatureWithEntry(m_creature, NPC_FELFIRE_SUMMONER, 175.0f))
1616  {
1617  summoner->CastSpell(pTarget, SPELL_SUMMON_FEL_FIRE, TRIGGERED_NONE);
1618  summoner->ForcedDespawn();
1619  }
1620  }
1621 
1622  /* Reset if:
1623  * Players run away (100 dist)
1624  * All players die
1625  * All players dead/dropped agro */
1626  bool IsPlayerOrGroupInRangeAndActiveInEvent()
1627  {
1628  for (Creature* soulstealer : m_lSoulstealers)
1629  {
1630  ThreatList const& threatList = soulstealer->getThreatManager().getThreatList();
1631 
1632  if (threatList.empty())
1633  return false;
1634  }
1635 
1636  if (Player* player = m_creature->GetMap()->GetPlayer(m_playerGuid)) // can find player
1637  {
1638  if (Group* group = player->GetGroup()) // player in group
1639  {
1640  for (GroupReference* ref = group->GetFirstMember(); ref != nullptr; ref = ref->next())
1641  {
1642  Player* member = ref->getSource(); // any member gettable, alive & in range
1643  if (member && member->IsAlive() && m_cHOFVisualTrigger && m_cHOFVisualTrigger->IsWithinDistInMap(member, MAX_PLAYER_DISTANCE))
1644  return true;
1645  }
1646  }
1647  else // player alone
1648  {
1649  if (player->IsAlive() && m_cHOFVisualTrigger && m_cHOFVisualTrigger->IsWithinDistInMap(player, MAX_PLAYER_DISTANCE))
1650  return true;
1651  }
1652  }
1653 
1654  return false;
1655  }
1656 
1657  void UpdateAI(const uint32 uiDiff) override
1658  {
1659  if (!m_bEventInProgress)
1660  return;
1661 
1662  if (m_bDeathwailGrounded)
1663  {
1664  if (!m_creature->SelectHostileTarget() || !m_creature->GetVictim())
1665  {
1666  if (m_uiDeathwailDespawnTimer < uiDiff)
1667  {
1668  m_creature->ForcedDespawn();
1669  m_creature->SetRespawnTime(60);
1670  }
1671  else
1672  m_uiDeathwailDespawnTimer -= uiDiff;
1673 
1674  return;
1675  }
1676 
1677  if (m_uiShadowBoltTimer < uiDiff)
1678  {
1679 
1680  if (DoCastSpellIfCan(m_creature->GetVictim(), SPELL_SHADOW_BOLT) == CAST_OK)
1681  m_uiShadowBoltTimer = SHADOW_BOLT_CD + urand(0, SHADOW_BOLT_CD);
1682  }
1683  else
1684  m_uiShadowBoltTimer -= uiDiff;
1685 
1686  if (m_uiShadowBoltVolleyTimer < uiDiff)
1687  {
1688  if (DoCastSpellIfCan(m_creature->GetVictim(), SPELL_SHADOW_BOLT_VOLLEY) == CAST_OK)
1689  m_uiShadowBoltVolleyTimer = SHADOW_BOLT_VOLLEY_CD + urand(0, SHADOW_BOLT_VOLLEY_CD);
1690  }
1691  else
1692  m_uiShadowBoltVolleyTimer -= uiDiff;
1693 
1694  if (m_uiFearTimer < uiDiff)
1695  {
1696  if (DoCastSpellIfCan(m_creature->GetVictim(), SPELL_FEAR) == CAST_OK)
1697  m_uiFearTimer = FEAR_CD + urand(0, FEAR_CD);
1698  }
1699  else
1700  m_uiFearTimer -= uiDiff;
1701 
1702  DoMeleeAttackIfReady();
1703  }
1704  else
1705  {
1706  // Check if event should reset
1707  if (m_playerGuid)
1708  {
1709  if (m_uiPlayerCheckTimer < uiDiff)
1710  {
1711  if (!IsPlayerOrGroupInRangeAndActiveInEvent())
1712  {
1713  DoReleaseSoulstealersAndReset();
1714  return;
1715  }
1716 
1717  m_uiPlayerCheckTimer = PLAYER_CHECK_CD;
1718  }
1719  else
1720  m_uiPlayerCheckTimer -= uiDiff;
1721  }
1722  else
1723  {
1724  DoReleaseSoulstealersAndReset();
1725  return;
1726  }
1727 
1728  if (m_uiFelFireballTimer < uiDiff)
1729  {
1730  if (m_cDeathwailTrigger)
1731  {
1732  if (m_creature->CastSpell(m_cDeathwailTrigger, SPELL_FEL_FIREBALL, TRIGGERED_NONE) == SPELL_CAST_OK)
1733  {
1734  // TODO: creature summoning should be handled by spell, not here?
1735  m_creature->SummonCreature(NPC_FELFIRE_SUMMONER,
1736  m_cDeathwailTrigger->GetPositionX(),
1737  m_cDeathwailTrigger->GetPositionY(),
1738  m_cDeathwailTrigger->GetPositionZ(), 0.0f, TEMPSPAWN_TIMED_DESPAWN, 6000, true);
1739  }
1740  }
1741 
1742  m_uiFelFireballTimer = FEL_FIREBALL_CD;
1743  }
1744  else
1745  m_uiFelFireballTimer -= uiDiff;
1746 
1747  if (m_uiPeriodicWaveTimer < uiDiff)
1748  {
1749  DoSummonWave();
1750  m_uiPeriodicWaveTimer = RETAINER_WAVE_CD;
1751  }
1752  else
1753  m_uiPeriodicWaveTimer -= uiDiff;
1754  }
1755  }
1756 };

1760  return new npc_shadowlord_deathwailAI(pCreature);

1807  bool exitCombat = false;
1808 
1809  if (m_cDeathwail)
1810  {
1811  if (npc_shadowlord_deathwailAI* DeathwailAI = dynamic_cast<npc_shadowlord_deathwailAI*>(m_cDeathwail->AI()))
1812  {
1813  if (!who->GetObjectGuid().IsPlayer()) // not attacked by player
1814  {
1815  if (Unit* attackerOwner = m_creature->GetMap()->GetPlayer(who->GetOwnerGuid()))
1816  who = attackerOwner;
1817  else // not attacked by player, nor NPC owned by player... just ignore
1818  exitCombat = true;
1819  }
1820  if (!exitCombat && DeathwailAI->SoulstealerEnteredCombat(m_creature, who))
1821  {
1822  m_creature->GetCombatManager().SetLeashingDisable(true);
1823  m_creature->AI()->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);
1824  }
1825  else
1826  exitCombat = true;
1827  }
1828  else
1829  exitCombat = true;
1830  }
1831  else
1832  exitCombat = true;
1833 
1834  if (exitCombat)
1835  m_creature->CombatStop();
1836  }
1837 
1838  void JustDied(Unit* /*killer*/) override
1839  {
1840  if (m_cDeathwail)
1841  if (npc_shadowlord_deathwailAI* DeathwailAI = dynamic_cast<npc_shadowlord_deathwailAI*>(m_cDeathwail->AI()))
1842  DeathwailAI->SoulstealerDied(m_creature);
1843  }
1844 
1845  void UpdateAI(const uint32 /*uiDiff*/) override
1846  {
1847  if (!m_creature->SelectHostileTarget())
1848  return;
1849 
1850  if (!m_cDeathwail)
1851  return;
1852 
1853  if (!m_bSixtyTriggered)
1854  {
1855  if (m_creature->GetHealthPercent() <= 60.0f)
1856  {
1857  if (npc_shadowlord_deathwailAI* DeathwailAI = dynamic_cast<npc_shadowlord_deathwailAI*>(m_cDeathwail->AI()))
1858  {
1859  DeathwailAI->DoSummonWave(true);
1860  m_bSixtyTriggered = true;
1861  }
1862  }
1863  }
1864  else if (!m_bTwentyTriggered)
1865  {
1866  if (m_creature->GetHealthPercent() <= 20.0f)
1867  {
1868  if (npc_shadowlord_deathwailAI* DeathwailAI = dynamic_cast<npc_shadowlord_deathwailAI*>(m_cDeathwail->AI()))
1869  {
1870  DeathwailAI->DoSummonWave(true);
1871  m_bTwentyTriggered = true;
1872  }
1873  }
1874  }
1875  }
1876 };

2200  void WaypointMotionType(uint32 /*motionType*/, uint32 pointId)
2201  {
2202  switch (pointId)
2203  {
2204  case WAYPOINT_ID_DESPAWN:
2205  {
2206  if (m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->GetPathId() == 2)
2207  {
2208  if (Creature* borak = GetSpeakerByEntry(NPC_BORAK_SON_OF_ORONOK))
2209  borak->ForcedDespawn();
2210  if (Creature* gromtor = GetSpeakerByEntry(NPC_GROMTOR_SON_OF_ORONOK))
2211  gromtor->ForcedDespawn();
2212  m_creature->ForcedDespawn();
2213  }
2214  break;
2215  }
2216  case WAYPOINT_ID_INTRO_FINAL:
2217  {
2218  // Set them in motion
2219  m_creature->SetWalk(false);
2220  m_creature->Mount(0);
2221  m_creature->SetLevitate(false);
2222  m_creature->SetHover(false);
2223  m_creature->Unmount();
2224  m_creature->StopMoving();
2225  m_creature->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(SPELL_ORONOK_SPEED_INCREASE);
2226  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->Clear(false, true);
2227  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->MoveIdle();
2228  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(POINT_ID_ATTACK_READY, aDamnationLocations[4].x, aDamnationLocations[4].y, aDamnationLocations[4].z);
2229  if (Creature* borak = GetSpeakerByEntry(NPC_BORAK_SON_OF_ORONOK))
2230  {
2231  borak->Mount(0);
2232  borak->SetLevitate(false);
2233  borak->SetHover(false);
2234  borak->Unmount();
2235  borak->GetMotionMaster()->MoveFollow(m_creature, 5.0f, -M_PI_F / 2, true);
2236  borak->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(SPELL_ORONOK_SPEED_INCREASE);
2237  m_borak = borak;
2238  }
2239  if (Creature* gromtor = GetSpeakerByEntry(NPC_GROMTOR_SON_OF_ORONOK))
2240  {
2241  gromtor->Mount(0);
2242  gromtor->SetLevitate(false);
2243  gromtor->SetHover(false);
2244  gromtor->Unmount();
2245  gromtor->GetMotionMaster()->MoveFollow(m_creature, 5.0f, M_PI_F / 2, true);
2246  gromtor->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(SPELL_ORONOK_SPEED_INCREASE);
2247  m_gromtor = gromtor;
2248  }
2249  if (Unit* summoner = m_creature->GetMap()->GetUnit(m_creature->GetSpawnerGuid()))
2250  DoScriptText(SAY_ORONOK_TOGETHER, m_creature, summoner);
2251  break;

2253  }

2256  void PointMovementInform(uint32 /*motionType*/, uint32 pointId)
2257  {
2258  switch (pointId)
2259  {
2260  case POINT_ID_ATTACK_READY:
2261  m_creature->SetFlag(UNIT_NPC_FLAGS, UNIT_NPC_FLAG_GOSSIP);
2262  DoScriptText(SAY_ORONOK_READY, m_creature);
2263  break;
2264  case POINT_ID_ELEMENTS:
2265  // Cyrukh starts to attack
2266  m_creature->setFaction(FACTION_ORONOK_COMBAT);
2267  if (Creature* borak = GetSpeakerByEntry(NPC_BORAK_SON_OF_ORONOK))
2268  borak->setFaction(FACTION_ORONOK_COMBAT);

2281  }
2282  break;

2324  {

2326  m_uiHealTimer = urand(6000, 10000);

2330

2401  {
2402  if (uiMoveType != POINT_MOTION_TYPE || !uiPointId)
2403  return;
2404

2413  {
2414  if (eventType == AI_EVENT_START_EVENT && pInvoker->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
2415  {
2416  DoScriptText(EMOTE_SNIFF_AIR, m_creature);
2417 
2418  float fX, fY, fZ;
2419  m_creature->SetWalk(false);
2420  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->MoveIdle();
2421  pSender->GetContactPoint(m_creature, fX, fY, fZ);
2422  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(1, fX, fY, fZ);
2423  }

2426  void UpdateAI(const uint32 uiDiff) override
2427  {
2428  if (m_uiTuberTimer)
2429  {
2430  if (m_uiTuberTimer <= uiDiff)
2431  {
2432  switch (m_uiTuberStage)
2433  {
2434  case 0:
2435  if (DoCastSpellIfCan(m_creature, SPELL_SPECIAL_UNARMED) == CAST_OK)
2436  m_uiTuberTimer = 2000;
2437  break;
2438  case 1:
2439  if (DoCastSpellIfCan(m_creature, SPELL_SHADOWMOON_TUBER) == CAST_OK)
2440  {
2441  // Despawn current tuber
2442  if (GameObject* pTuber = GetClosestGameObjectWithEntry(m_creature, GO_SHADOWMOON_TUBER_MOUND, 3.0f))
2443  pTuber->SetLootState(GO_JUST_DEACTIVATED);
2444 
2445  DoScriptText(EMOTE_SQUEAL, m_creature);
2446  m_uiTuberTimer = 2000;
2447  }
2448  break;
2449  case 2:
2450  EnterEvadeMode();
2451  break;
2452  }
2453  ++m_uiTuberStage;
2454  }
2455  else
2456  m_uiTuberTimer -= uiDiff;
2457  }
2458 
2459  if (!m_creature->SelectHostileTarget() || !m_creature->GetVictim())
2460  return;
2461 
2462  DoMeleeAttackIfReady();
2463  }
2464 };

2471 bool EffectDummyCreature_npc_shadowmoon_tuber_node(Unit* pCaster, uint32 uiSpellId, SpellEffectIndex uiEffIndex, Creature* pCreatureTarget, ObjectGuid /*originalCasterGuid*/)
2472 {
2473  // always check spellid and effectindex

2475  {
2476  if (pCreatureTarget->GetEntry() == NPC_SHADOWMOON_TUBER_NODE)
2477  {
2478  // Check if tuber mound exists or it's spawned
2479  GameObject* pTuber = GetClosestGameObjectWithEntry(pCreatureTarget, GO_SHADOWMOON_TUBER_MOUND, 1.0f);
2480  if (!pTuber || !pTuber->IsSpawned())
2481  return true;
2482 
2483  // Call nearby felboar
2484  if (Creature* pBoar = GetClosestCreatureWithEntry(pCreatureTarget, NPC_DOMESTICATED_FELBOAR, 40.0f))
2485  pCreatureTarget->AI()->SendAIEvent(AI_EVENT_START_EVENT, pCaster, pBoar);
2486  }
2487 
2488  // always return true when we are handling this spell and effect
2489  return true;
2490  }
2491 
2492  return false;
2493 }

2600  if (node)
2601  {
2602  float angle = m_creature->GetAngle(node);
2603  m_creature->SetOrientation(angle);

2610  m_creature->UpdateEntry(NPC_PEON);

2612  m_creature->ForcedDespawn(90000);

2614  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->MoveIdle();
2615  }

2619  void SpellHit(Unit* caster, const SpellEntry* spell) override
2620  {

2622  HandleBooterang(caster);
2623  }
2624 
2625  void HandleAngry()
2626  {
2627  DoCastSpellIfCan(nullptr, SPELL_DEFIANT_AND_ENRAGED);
2628  switch (urand(0, 4))
2629  {
2630  case 0: DoScriptText(SAY_IDLE1, m_creature); break;
2631  case 1: DoScriptText(SAY_IDLE2, m_creature); break;
2632  default: break;
2633  }
2634  }
2635 
2636  void HandleBooterang(Unit* caster)
2637  {
2638  if (caster->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER && m_lastPlayerGuid.IsEmpty())
2639  return;
2640 
2641  Player* player = static_cast<Player*>(caster);
2642  m_lastPlayerGuid = player->GetObjectGuid();
2643 
2644  switch (urand(0, 5))
2645  {
2646  case 0: DoScriptText(SAY_BOOTERANG1, m_creature, player); break;
2647  case 1: DoScriptText(SAY_BOOTERANG2, m_creature, player); break;
2648  case 2: DoScriptText(SAY_BOOTERANG3, m_creature, player); break;
2649  case 3: DoScriptText(SAY_BOOTERANG4, m_creature, player); break;
2650  case 4: DoScriptText(SAY_BOOTERANG5, m_creature, player); break;
2651  case 5: DoScriptText(SAY_BOOTERANG6, m_creature, player); break;
2652  }
2653  float angle = m_creature->GetAngle(player);
2654  m_creature->SetOrientation(angle);
2655  m_creature->SetFacingTo(angle);
2656 
2657  DoCastSpellIfCan(nullptr, SPELL_PEON_CLEAR_ALL); // clears combat and removes aura
2658  m_creature->setFaction(FACTION_WHACKED);
2659 
2660  m_booterangTimer = 3000;
2661  m_angryTimer = 0;
2662  }
2663 
2664  void UpdateAI(const uint32 diff) override
2665  {
2666  if (!m_creature->IsInCombat())
2667  {
2668  if (m_angryTimer)
2669  {
2670  if (m_angryTimer <= diff)
2671  {
2672  HandleAngry();
2673  m_angryTimer = urand(6000, 10000);
2674  }
2675  else m_angryTimer -= diff;
2676  }
2677 
2678  if (m_booterangTimer)
2679  {
2680  if (m_booterangTimer <= diff)
2681  {
2682  float x, y, z;
2683  Creature* node = GetClosestCreatureWithEntry(m_creature, NPC_PEON_WORK_NODE, 60.f);
2684  if (node)
2685  node->GetNearPoint(m_creature, x, y, z, m_creature->GetObjectBoundingRadius(), 5.f, node->GetAngle(m_creature));
2686  else // failsafe
2687  m_creature->GetPosition(x, y, z);
2688  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(POINT_ARRIVED, x, y, z);
2689  m_booterangTimer = 0;
2690  }
2691  else m_booterangTimer -= diff;
2692  }
2693  }
2694  else
2695  {
2696  if (!m_creature->SelectHostileTarget() || !m_creature->GetVictim())
2697  return;
2698 
2699  if (m_kickTimer)
2700  {
2701  if (m_kickTimer <= diff)
2702  {
2703  if (DoCastSpellIfCan(m_creature->GetVictim(), SPELL_KICK) == CAST_OK)
2704  m_kickTimer = urand(12000, 24000);
2705  }
2706  else m_kickTimer -= diff;
2707  }
2708  if (m_sunderarmorTimer)
2709  {
2710  if (m_sunderarmorTimer <= diff)
2711  {
2712  if (DoCastSpellIfCan(m_creature->GetVictim(), SPELL_SUNDER_ARMOR) == CAST_OK)
2713  m_sunderarmorTimer = urand(12000, 18000);
2714  }
2715  else m_sunderarmorTimer -= diff;
2716  }
2717 
2718  DoMeleeAttackIfReady();
2719  }
2720 
2721  ScriptedAI::UpdateAI(diff);
2722  }
2723 };

2872 struct npc_commanderAI : public CombatAI
2873 {
2874  npc_commanderAI(Creature* creature, uint8 commanderId) : CombatAI(creature, COMMANDER_COMBAT_ACTION_MAX),
2875  m_defenderSpawns(DEFENDER_SPAWN_COUNT),
2876  m_dragonmawSpawns(DRAGONMAW_SPAWN_COUNT),
2877  m_killCounter(0),
2878  m_commanderId(commanderId)
2879  {
2880  m_attackDistance = 30.f;
2881  m_meleeEnabled = false;
2882  AddCombatAction(COMMANDER_COMBAT_ACTION_AIMED_SHOT, GetInitialCombatActionTimer(COMMANDER_COMBAT_ACTION_AIMED_SHOT));
2883  AddCombatAction(COMMANDER_COMBAT_ACTION_MULTI_SHOT, GetInitialCombatActionTimer(COMMANDER_COMBAT_ACTION_MULTI_SHOT));
2884  AddCombatAction(COMMANDER_COMBAT_ACTION_SHOOT, GetInitialCombatActionTimer(COMMANDER_COMBAT_ACTION_SHOOT));
2885 
2886  AddCustomAction(COMMANDER_ACTION_START_QUEST_FLAGS, true, [&]() { m_creature->RemoveFlag(UNIT_NPC_FLAGS, UNIT_NPC_FLAG_QUESTGIVER); });
2887  AddCustomAction(COMMANDER_ACTION_START_QUEST_TEXT, true, [&]()
2888  { DoScriptText(deadliestScriptInfo[m_commanderId].startText, m_creature, m_creature->GetMap()->GetPlayer(m_startingPlayer)); });
2889  AddCustomAction(COMMANDER_ACTION_START_QUEST_MOVEMENT, true, [&]() { m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->MoveWaypoint(); });
2890  AddCustomAction(COMMANDER_ACTION_POST_MOVEMENT_TEXT, true, [&]()
2891  { DoScriptText(deadliestScriptInfo[m_commanderId].midText, m_creature, m_creature->GetMap()->GetPlayer(m_startingPlayer)); });
2892  AddCustomAction(COMMANDER_ACTION_POST_MOVEMENT_START_EVENT, true, [&]() { StartAttackingEvent(); });
2893  AddCustomAction(COMMANDER_ACTION_WIN_RETURN, true, [&]()
2894  {
2895  float x, y, z, ori;
2896  m_creature->GetRespawnCoord(x, y, z, &ori);
2897  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(POINT_HOME, x, y, z);
2898  });
2899  AddCustomAction(COMMANDER_ACTION_FAIL_EVENT, true, [&]()
2900  {
2901  m_creature->ForcedDespawn();
2902  FailEvent();
2903  });
2904  }
2905 
2906  GuidVector m_defenderSpawns;
2907  GuidVector m_dragonmawSpawns;
2908  ObjectGuid m_startingPlayer;
2909 
2910  uint8 m_killCounter;
2911  uint8 m_commanderId;

2913  void GetAIInformation(ChatHandler& reader) override
2914  {
2915  ScriptedAI::GetAIInformation(reader);
2916  CombatActions::GetAIInformation(reader);
2917  reader.PSendSysMessage("Defender Spawn Count: %lu", m_defenderSpawns.size());
2918  reader.PSendSysMessage("Dragonmaw Spawn Count: %lu", m_dragonmawSpawns.size());
2919  reader.PSendSysMessage("Starting player: %lu", m_startingPlayer.GetRawValue());
2920  reader.PSendSysMessage("Kill counter: %u", m_killCounter);
2921  }
2922 
2923  uint32 GetInitialCombatActionTimer(uint32 index)
2924  {
2925  switch (index)
2926  {
2927  case COMMANDER_COMBAT_ACTION_AIMED_SHOT: return 5000;
2928  case COMMANDER_COMBAT_ACTION_MULTI_SHOT: return 10000;
2929  case COMMANDER_COMBAT_ACTION_SHOOT: return 0;
2930  }
2931  return 0;
2932  }
2933 
2934  uint32 GetRepeatingCombatActionTimer(uint32 index)
2935  {
2936  switch (index)
2937  {
2938  case COMMANDER_COMBAT_ACTION_AIMED_SHOT: return 10000;
2939  case COMMANDER_COMBAT_ACTION_MULTI_SHOT: return 15000;
2940  case COMMANDER_COMBAT_ACTION_SHOOT: return 3000;
2941  }
2942  return 0;
2943  }
2944 
2945  void ExecuteAction(uint32 action) override
2946  {
2947  switch (action)
2948  {
2949  case COMMANDER_COMBAT_ACTION_AIMED_SHOT:
2950  if (DoCastSpellIfCan(m_creature->GetVictim(), SPELL_AIMED_SHOT) == CAST_OK)
2951  ResetCombatAction(action, GetRepeatingCombatActionTimer(action));
2952  return;
2953  case COMMANDER_COMBAT_ACTION_MULTI_SHOT:
2954  if (DoCastSpellIfCan(m_creature->GetVictim(), SPELL_MULTI_SHOT) == CAST_OK)
2955  ResetCombatAction(action, GetRepeatingCombatActionTimer(action));
2956  return;
2957  case COMMANDER_COMBAT_ACTION_SHOOT:
2958  if (DoCastSpellIfCan(m_creature->GetVictim(), SPELL_SHOOT) == CAST_OK)
2959  ResetCombatAction(action, GetRepeatingCombatActionTimer(action));
2960  return;
2961  }
2962  }
2963 
2964  void SpawnDefenders()
2965  {
2966  for (uint32 i = 0; i < DEFENDER_SPAWN_COUNT; ++i)
2967  {
2968  Creature* defender = m_creature->SummonCreature(deadliestScriptInfo[m_commanderId].defenderNpc, defenderSpawns[m_commanderId][i].x,
2969  defenderSpawns[m_commanderId][i].y, defenderSpawns[m_commanderId][i].z, defenderSpawns[m_commanderId][i].ori, TEMPSPAWN_CORPSE_DESPAWN, 1000, true);
2970  defender->HandleEmote(EMOTE_STATE_READYRIFLE);
2971  m_defenderSpawns[i] = defender->GetObjectGuid();
2972  }
2973  }
2974 
2975  void DespawnDefenders()
2976  {
2977  for (ObjectGuid& guid : m_defenderSpawns)
2978  if (Creature* defender = m_creature->GetMap()->GetCreature(guid))
2979  defender->ForcedDespawn();
2980  }

2985  SpawnSpecificDragonmaw(i);
2986  }
2987 
2988  void SpawnSpecificDragonmaw(uint32 i)
2989  {
2990  Creature* dragonmaw = m_creature->SummonCreature(deadliestScriptInfo[m_commanderId].dragonmawNpc, dragonmawSpawns[m_commanderId][i].x,
2991  dragonmawSpawns[m_commanderId][i].y, dragonmawSpawns[m_commanderId][i].z, dragonmawSpawns[m_commanderId][i].ori, TEMPSPAWN_CORPSE_DESPAWN, 1000, true, true, i);
2992  m_dragonmawSpawns[i] = dragonmaw->GetObjectGuid();
2993  }

2996  {
2997  for (ObjectGuid& guid : m_dragonmawSpawns)
2998  if (Creature* dragonmaw = m_creature->GetMap()->GetCreature(guid))
2999  dragonmaw->ForcedDespawn();
3000  }

3002  void StartEvent(Player* player)
3003  {
3004  m_startingPlayer = player->GetObjectGuid();
3005  SpawnDefenders();
3006  m_killCounter = 0;
3007  m_creature->SetWalk(false);
3008  ResetTimer(COMMANDER_ACTION_START_QUEST_FLAGS, 1000);
3009  ResetTimer(COMMANDER_ACTION_START_QUEST_TEXT, 2000);
3010  ResetTimer(COMMANDER_ACTION_START_QUEST_MOVEMENT, 4500);
3011  m_creature->SetActiveObjectState(true);
3012  }
3013 
3014  virtual void FinishedWaypointMovement()
3015  {
3016  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->Clear(false, true);
3017  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->MoveIdle();
3018  m_creature->SetSheath(SHEATH_STATE_RANGED);
3019  ResetTimer(COMMANDER_ACTION_FAIL_EVENT, 900000);
3020  }
3021 
3022  virtual void StartAttackingEvent()
3023  {
3024  SpawnDragonmaw();
3025  }
3026 
3027  void WinEvent()
3028  {
3029  if (Player* player = m_creature->GetMap()->GetPlayer(m_startingPlayer))
3030  player->RewardPlayerAndGroupAtEventExplored(deadliestScriptInfo[m_commanderId].questId, m_creature);
3031 
3032  DoScriptText(deadliestScriptInfo[m_commanderId].winText, m_creature, m_creature->GetMap()->GetPlayer(m_startingPlayer));
3033 
3034  if (m_creature->IsInCombat())
3035  EnterEvadeMode();
3036  ResetTimer(COMMANDER_ACTION_WIN_RETURN, 3000);
3037  ResetEvent();
3038  }
3039 
3040  void FailEvent()
3041  {
3042  DoScriptText(deadliestScriptInfo[m_commanderId].deathText, m_creature, m_creature->GetMap()->GetPlayer(m_startingPlayer));
3043  ResetEvent();
3044  }
3045 
3046  void ResetEvent()
3047  {
3048  DespawnDefenders();
3049  DespawnDragonmaw();
3050  m_startingPlayer = ObjectGuid();
3051  m_creature->SetSheath(SHEATH_STATE_MELEE);
3052  DisableTimer(COMMANDER_ACTION_FAIL_EVENT);
3053  m_creature->HandleEmote(0);
3054  m_creature->SetActiveObjectState(false);
3055  }
3056 
3057  void JustDied(Unit* /*killer*/) override
3058  {
3059  FailEvent();
3060  }
3061 
3062  void MovementInform(uint32 movementType, uint32 data) override
3063  {
3064  switch (movementType)
3065  {
3066  case WAYPOINT_MOTION_TYPE:
3067  if (deadliestScriptInfo[m_commanderId].lastPointInPath == data)
3068  FinishedWaypointMovement();
3069  break;
3070  case POINT_MOTION_TYPE:
3071  if (data == POINT_HOME)
3072  {
3073  float x, y, z, ori;
3074  m_creature->GetRespawnCoord(x, y, z, &ori);
3075  m_creature->SetOrientation(ori); m_creature->SetFacingTo(ori);
3076  m_creature->SetFlag(UNIT_NPC_FLAGS, UNIT_NPC_FLAG_QUESTGIVER);
3077  }
3078  break;
3079  }
3080  }
3081 
3082  void SummonedCreatureJustDied(Creature* summoned) override
3083  {
3084  if (summoned->GetEntry() == deadliestScriptInfo[m_commanderId].dragonmawNpc)
3085  {
3086  ++m_killCounter;
3087  if (m_killCounter >= DRAGONMAW_KILL_COUNT)
3088  {
3089  WinEvent();
3090  return;
3091  }
3092  ObjectGuid const& guid = summoned->GetObjectGuid();
3093  for (uint32 i = 0; i < m_dragonmawSpawns.size(); ++i)
3094  {
3095  if (guid == m_dragonmawSpawns[i])
3096  {
3097  SpawnSpecificDragonmaw(i);
3098  break;
3099  }
3100  }
3101  }
3102  }
3103 
3104  void UpdateAI(const uint32 diff) override
3105  {
3106  UpdateTimers(diff, m_creature->IsInCombat());
3107 
3108  if (!m_creature->SelectHostileTarget() || !m_creature->GetVictim())
3109  return;
3110 
3111  ExecuteActions();
3112  }

3156 bool QuestAccept_npc_commander(Player* player, Creature* questgiver, Quest const* quest)
3157 {
3158  switch (quest->GetQuestId())
3159  {
3160  case QUEST_DEADLIEST_TRAP_SCRYERS:
3161  case QUEST_DEADLIEST_TRAP_ALDOR:
3162  if (npc_commanderAI* ai = static_cast<npc_commanderAI*>(questgiver->AI()))
3163  ai->StartEvent(player);
3164  return true;
3165  }
3166 
3167  return false;
3168 }

3325  virtual void AttackPlayer()
3326  {
3327  if (Player* pPlayer = m_creature->GetMap()->GetPlayer(m_playerRacerGuid))
3328  {
3329  float fX, fY, fZ;
3330  m_creature->GetRandomPoint(m_creature->GetPositionX(), m_creature->GetPositionY(), m_creature->GetPositionZ(), 15.0f, fX, fY, fZ);

3332  m_creature->GetRandomPoint(pPlayer->GetPositionX(), pPlayer->GetPositionY(), pPlayer->GetPositionZ(), 10.0f, fX, fY, fZ);
3333  m_creature->SummonCreature(dragonmawRacesScriptInfo[m_racerId].targetNpc, fX, fY, fZ, 0, TEMPSPAWN_TIMED_DESPAWN, 6000);
3334  }

3336  }

3339  {

3341  m_creature->SetLevitate(false);

3346  {
3347  DoScriptText(dragonmawRacesScriptInfo[m_racerId].winText, m_creature, pPlayer);
3348  pPlayer->RewardPlayerAndGroupAtEventExplored(dragonmawRacesScriptInfo[m_racerId].questId, m_creature);
3349  }

3543 bool QuestAccept_npc_dragonmaw_racer(Player* player, Creature* questgiver, Quest const* quest)
3544 {
3545  switch (quest->GetQuestId())
3546  {
3547  case QUEST_MUCKJAW:
3548  case QUEST_TROPE:
3549  case QUEST_CORLOK:
3550  case QUEST_ICHMAN:
3551  case QUEST_MULVERICK:
3552  case QUEST_SKYSHATTER:
3553  if (npc_dragonmaw_racerAI* ai = static_cast<npc_dragonmaw_racerAI*>(questgiver->AI()))
3554  {
3555  DoScriptText(dragonmawRacesScriptInfo[ai->m_racerId].startText, questgiver, player);
3556  ai->m_playerRacerGuid = player->GetObjectGuid();
3557  ai->m_questId = quest->GetQuestId();
3558  questgiver->SetUInt32Value(UNIT_NPC_FLAGS, UNIT_NPC_FLAG_NONE);
3559  questgiver->GetMotionMaster()->MovePath(0, PATH_FROM_EXTERNAL);
3560  }
3561  return true;
3562  }
3563 
3564  return false;
3565 }

3567 struct DragonmawKnockdownTheAggroCheck : public SpellScript
3568 {
3569  void OnEffectExecute(Spell* spell, SpellEffectIndex /*effIdx*/) const override
3570  {
3571  if (!spell->GetUnitTarget()->IsPlayer() || spell->GetCaster()->IsPlayer())
3572  return;
3573 
3574  if (npc_dragonmaw_racerAI* ai = static_cast<npc_dragonmaw_racerAI*>(spell->GetCaster()->AI()))
3575  if (((Player*)spell->GetUnitTarget())->GetObjectGuid() == ai->m_playerRacerGuid)
3576  spell->SetScriptValue(1); // found player within 100 yds still - race may continue
3577  }
3578 
3579  void OnSuccessfulFinish(Spell* spell) const override
3580  {
3581  if (spell->GetCaster()->IsPlayer())
3582  return;
3583 
3584  if (!spell->GetScriptValue()) // lost race - player got too far away
3585  if (npc_dragonmaw_racerAI* ai = static_cast<npc_dragonmaw_racerAI*>(spell->GetCaster()->AI()))
3586  ai->FailRace();
3587  }
3588 };

3848  uint32 GetInitialActionTimer(const uint32 action) const
3849  {
3850  switch (m_creature->GetEntry())
3851  {
3852  case NPC_ILLIDARI_RAVAGER:
3853  {
3854  switch (action)
3855  {
3856  case ILLIDARI_CLEAVE: return urand(4000, 7000);
3857  case ILLIDARI_CUTDOWN: return 6000;
3858  case ILLIDARI_DEMORALIZING_SHOUT: return 8000;
3859  default: return 0;
3860  }
3861  }
3862  case NPC_SHADOWHOOF_ASSASSIN:
3863  {
3864  switch (action)
3865  {
3866  case ASSASSIN_DEBILITATING_STRIKE: return urand(3500, 4000);
3867  case ASSASSIN_SINISTER_STRIKE: return urand(6000, 8000);
3868  default: return 0;
3869  }
3870  }
3871  case NPC_ILLIDARI_SUCCUBUS:
3872  {
3873  switch (action)
3874  {
3875  case SUCCUBUS_LASH_OF_PAIN: return urand(2000, 4000);
3876  case SUCCUBUS_SEDUCTION: return urand(5000, 14000);
3877  default: return 0;
3878  }
3879  }
3880  case NPC_LIGHTSWORN_VINDICATOR:
3881  {
3882  switch (action)
3883  {
3884  case VINDICATOR_EXORCISM: return urand(3000, 12000);
3885  case VINDICATOR_HAMMER: return urand(5000, 15000);
3886  case VINDICATOR_HOLY_LIGHT: return urand(2500, 4000);
3887  case VINDICATOR_SEAL_OF_SAC: return urand(1000, 4000);
3888  default: return 0;
3889  }
3890  }
3891  case NPC_ANCHORITE_CAALEN:
3892  {
3893  switch (action)
3894  {
3895  case CAALEN_HOLY_SMITE: return urand(3000, 9000);
3896  case CAALEN_PRAYER_OF_HEALING: return urand(9000, 12000);
3897  default: return 0;
3898  }
3899  }

4352 struct FormationMap
4353 {
4354  std::map<ObjectGuid, ObjectGuid> markerToOccupant;
4355  std::map<ObjectGuid, ObjectGuid> occupantToMarker;
4356 
4357  void clearMaps()
4358  {
4359  markerToOccupant.clear();
4360  occupantToMarker.clear();
4361  }
4362 
4363  void registerFormationMarker(ObjectGuid marker)
4364  {
4365  markerToOccupant[marker] = ObjectGuid();
4366  }
4367 
4368  // Returns the marker claimed
4369  ObjectGuid claimFormationMarker(ObjectGuid occupant)
4370  {
4371  if (occupant.IsEmpty())
4372  return ObjectGuid();
4373 
4374  if (occupantToMarker.count(occupant))
4375  return occupantToMarker[occupant];
4376 
4377  std::vector<ObjectGuid> openMarkers;
4378 
4379  for (std::map<ObjectGuid, ObjectGuid>::iterator itr = markerToOccupant.begin(); itr != markerToOccupant.end(); ++itr)
4380  if (itr->second.IsEmpty())
4381  openMarkers.push_back(itr->first);
4382 
4383  ObjectGuid marker;
4384 
4385  if (openMarkers.size() > 0)
4386  {
4387  marker = openMarkers[urand(0, openMarkers.size() - 1)];
4388 
4389  markerToOccupant[marker] = occupant;
4390  occupantToMarker[occupant] = marker;
4391 
4392  return marker;
4393  }
4394  else
4395  return marker;
4396  }
4397 
4398  bool releaseFormationMarker(ObjectGuid occupant)
4399  {
4400  if (!occupantToMarker.count(occupant))
4401  return false;
4402 
4403  markerToOccupant[occupantToMarker[occupant]] = ObjectGuid();
4404  occupantToMarker.erase(occupant);
4405  return true;
4406  }
4407 
4408  ObjectGuid getRandomOccupant()
4409  {
4410  if (occupantToMarker.empty())
4411  return ObjectGuid();
4412 
4413  uint32 chance = occupantToMarker.size();
4414  for (auto itr = occupantToMarker.begin(); itr != occupantToMarker.end(); ++itr)
4415  {
4416  if (urand(0, chance--) == 0)
4417  return itr->first;
4418  }
4419 
4420  return ObjectGuid();
4421  }
4422 
4423  void EngageInBlackTempleAssault(int numberTroops, int point, Map* map)
4424  {
4425  int count = 0;
4426 
4427  GuidVector guids;
4428 
4429  for (auto itr = occupantToMarker.begin(); itr != occupantToMarker.end(); ++itr)
4430  {
4431  if (Creature* occupant = map->GetCreature(itr->first))
4432  {
4433  if (occupant->IsInCombat())
4434  continue;
4435 
4436  occupant->GetMotionMaster()->Clear(false, true);
4437  occupant->GetMotionMaster()->MoveWaypoint(0, 2);
4438  occupant->GetMotionMaster()->SetNextWaypoint(point);
4439  occupant->SetWalk(false);
4440 
4441  if (mob_bt_battle_fighterAI* occupantAI = dynamic_cast<mob_bt_battle_fighterAI*>(occupant->AI()))
4442  occupantAI->m_bIsWaypointing = true;
4443 
4444  guids.push_back(itr->first);
4445 
4446  ++count;
4447  }
4448 
4449  if (count >= numberTroops)
4450  break;
4451  }
4452 
4453  for (ObjectGuid guid : guids)
4454  releaseFormationMarker(guid);
4455  }
4456 };

4541  void ReceiveAIEvent(AIEventType eventType, Unit* sender, Unit* /*invoker*/, uint32 /*miscValue*/) override
4542  {
4543  const ObjectGuid senderGuid = sender->GetObjectGuid();
4544 
4545  switch (sender->GetEntry())
4546  {
4547  case NPC_ILLIDARI_RAVAGER:
4548  /* Expected events:
4549  * A: Ravager group 1 ready
4550  * B: Ravager group 2 ready
4551  * C: Ravager group 3 ready
4552  * D: Ravager group 4 ready
4553  * E: Left Ravager leader spawned
4554  * F: Right Ravager leader spawned
4555  * Custom_A: Attack */
4556  switch (eventType)
4557  {
4558  case AI_EVENT_JUST_DIED:
4559  m_fIllidariAttackTimer *= 0.75f;
4560  break;
4561  case AI_EVENT_CUSTOM_EVENTAI_A:
4562  if (Creature* leader = m_creature->GetMap()->GetCreature(m_ravagerLeader1))
4563  {

4985  void IllidariAttackNearestEnemy(Unit* attacker)
4986  {
4987  Creature* nearestLightsworn;
4988  Creature* nearestMagister;
4989 
4990  nearestLightsworn = GetClosestCreatureWithEntry(attacker, NPC_LIGHTSWORN_VINDICATOR, 55.0f);
4991  nearestMagister = GetClosestCreatureWithEntry(attacker, NPC_SEASONED_MAGISTER, 55.0f);
4992 
4993  if (!nearestLightsworn && !nearestMagister)
4994  return;
4995 
4996  float distLightsworn = ((nearestLightsworn == nullptr) ? 9999.0f : attacker->GetDistance(nearestLightsworn));
4997 
4998  if (nearestMagister)
4999  {
5000  float distMagister = attacker->GetDistance(nearestMagister);
5001  nearestLightsworn = (distLightsworn < distMagister) ? nearestLightsworn : nearestMagister;
5002  }
5003 
5004  attacker->AI()->AttackStart(nearestLightsworn);
5005  }

5007  ObjectGuid GetAvailableMarkerFromMap(FormationMap& map, ObjectGuid occupant)
5008  {
5009  ObjectGuid marker = map.claimFormationMarker(occupant);
5010 
5011  if (!marker.IsEmpty())
5012  return marker;
5013  else
5014  {
5015  FindFormationMarkers();
5016  return map.claimFormationMarker(occupant);
5017  }
5018  }
5019 
5020  bool FindFormationMarkers()
5021  {
5022  m_rearFormationMapScryer.clearMaps();
5023  m_rearFormationMapAldor.clearMaps();
5024  std::list<Creature*> lFormationMarkers;
5025 
5026  GetCreatureListWithEntryInGrid(lFormationMarkers, m_creature, NPC_FORMATION_MARKER, 300.0f);
5027 
5028  for (std::list<Creature*>::iterator itr = lFormationMarkers.begin(); itr != lFormationMarkers.end(); ++itr)
5029  if ((*itr)->GetPositionY() < 540.0f)
5030  m_forwardFormationMap.registerFormationMarker((*itr)->GetObjectGuid());
5031  else
5032  {
5033  bool left_side = ((*itr)->GetPositionX() < m_fMidPoint);
5034  bool CaalenFyra = ((*itr)->GetPositionY() > 582.5f);
5035 
5036  if (left_side)
5037  {
5038  if (CaalenFyra)
5039  m_fyraGuid = (*itr)->GetObjectGuid();
5040  else
5041  m_rearFormationMapScryer.registerFormationMarker((*itr)->GetObjectGuid());
5042  }
5043  else
5044  {
5045  if (CaalenFyra)
5046  m_caalenGuid = (*itr)->GetObjectGuid();
5047  else
5048  m_rearFormationMapAldor.registerFormationMarker((*itr)->GetObjectGuid());
5049  }
5050  }
5051 
5052  if (lFormationMarkers.size() > 0)
5053  return true;
5054 
5055  return false;
5056  }
5057 
5058  void ReinforceAldorScryerFrontline()
5059  {
5060  while ((m_uiNumLightswornForward + m_uiNumMagisterForward) < m_uiMaxNumTroopsForward)
5061  {
5062  ObjectGuid fighter;
5063 
5064  if (urand(0, m_uiMaxNumTroopsForward + m_uiNumLightswornForward - m_uiNumMagisterForward) < m_uiMaxNumTroopsForward)
5065  fighter = m_rearFormationMapAldor.getRandomOccupant();
5066  else
5067  fighter = m_rearFormationMapScryer.getRandomOccupant();
5068 
5069  if (fighter.IsEmpty())
5070  return;
5071 
5072  ObjectGuid marker = GetAvailableMarkerFromMap(m_forwardFormationMap, fighter);
5073 
5074  if (!marker.IsEmpty())
5075  if (Creature* fighterCreature = m_creature->GetMap()->GetCreature(fighter))
5076  if (!fighterCreature->IsInCombat())
5077  if (Creature* markerCreature = m_creature->GetMap()->GetCreature(marker))
5078  {
5079  fighterCreature->GetMotionMaster()->Clear(false, true);
5080  fighterCreature->SetWalk(false);
5081  fighterCreature->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(0, markerCreature->GetPositionX(), markerCreature->GetPositionY(), markerCreature->GetPositionZ());
5082 
5083  if (fighterCreature->GetEntry() == NPC_LIGHTSWORN_VINDICATOR)
5084  {
5085  ++m_uiNumLightswornForward;
5086  m_rearFormationMapAldor.releaseFormationMarker(fighter);
5087  }
5088  else
5089  {
5090  ++m_uiNumMagisterForward;
5091  m_rearFormationMapScryer.releaseFormationMarker(fighter);
5092  }
5093  }
5094 
5095  fighter.Clear();
5096  marker.Clear();
5097  }
5098  }
5099 
5100  void SendIllidariAttack()
5101  {
5102  IllidariAttackGroup attackGroup = ChooseIllidariAttack();
5103  ObjectGuid leaderGuid;
5104  uint32 waypoint = 0;
5105 
5106  switch (attackGroup)
5107  {
5108  case NONE:
5109  break;
5110  case RAVAGERS_1:
5111  leaderGuid = m_ravagerLeader1;
5112  m_ravagerLeader1.Clear();
5113  waypoint = 5;
5114  break;
5115  case RAVAGERS_2:
5116  leaderGuid = m_ravagerLeader2;
5117  m_ravagerLeader2.Clear();
5118  waypoint = 5;
5119  break;
5120  case RAVAGERS_3:
5121  leaderGuid = m_ravagerLeader3;
5122  m_ravagerLeader3.Clear();
5123  waypoint = 3;
5124  break;
5125  case RAVAGERS_4:
5126  leaderGuid = m_ravagerLeader4;
5127  m_ravagerLeader4.Clear();
5128  waypoint = 3;
5129  break;
5130  case SHADOWHOOF_1:
5131  leaderGuid = m_ShadowhoofLeader1;
5132  m_ShadowhoofLeader1.Clear();
5133  waypoint = 5;
5134  break;
5135  case SHADOWHOOF_2:
5136  leaderGuid = m_ShadowhoofLeader2;
5137  m_ShadowhoofLeader2.Clear();
5138  waypoint = 3;
5139  break;
5140  case SHADOWHOOF_3:
5141  leaderGuid = m_ShadowhoofLeader3;
5142  m_ShadowhoofLeader3.Clear();
5143  waypoint = 4;
5144  break;
5145  }
5146 
5147  if (Creature* leader = m_creature->GetMap()->GetCreature(leaderGuid))
5148  {
5149  leader->GetMotionMaster()->Clear(false, true);
5150  leader->GetMotionMaster()->MoveWaypoint(0, 1);
5151  leader->GetMotionMaster()->SetNextWaypoint(waypoint);
5152  leader->ForcedDespawn(600000);
5153  m_attackReadyMask -= attackGroup;
5154 
5155  if (mob_bt_battle_fighterAI* leaderAI = dynamic_cast<mob_bt_battle_fighterAI*>(leader->AI()))
5156  leaderAI->m_bIsWaypointing = true;
5157  }
5158  }
5159 
5160  // Determine how many waves are ready
5161  int countSetBits(uint8 n)
5162  {
5163  // base case
5164  if (n == 0)
5165  return 0;
5166  else
5167  // if last bit set add 1 else add 0
5168  return (n & 1) + countSetBits(n >> 1);
5169  }
5170 
5171  /* Most of the time send ravager group 3 or 4
5172  * rest of the time send one of the others randomly */
5173  IllidariAttackGroup ChooseIllidariAttack()
5174  {
5175  if (countSetBits(m_attackReadyMask) < m_uiMinAttackGroupsReady)
5176  return NONE;
5177  else
5178  {
5179  uint8 rav3or4_mask = m_attackReadyMask & (RAVAGERS_3 | RAVAGERS_4);
5180  uint8 everythingElse_mask = m_attackReadyMask & ~(RAVAGERS_3 | RAVAGERS_4);
5181 
5182  if (rav3or4_mask && !everythingElse_mask)
5183  {
5184  return ChooseIllidariRavagers3or4(rav3or4_mask);
5185  }
5186  else if (!rav3or4_mask && everythingElse_mask)
5187  {
5188  return ChooseIllidariNotRavagers3or4(everythingElse_mask);
5189  }
5190  else
5191  {
5192  if (urand(0, 9) >= 3)
5193  return ChooseIllidariRavagers3or4(rav3or4_mask);
5194  else
5195  return ChooseIllidariNotRavagers3or4(everythingElse_mask);
5196  }
5197  }
5198 
5199  return NONE;
5200  }
5201 
5202  IllidariAttackGroup ChooseIllidariRavagers3or4(uint8 readyMask)
5203  {
5204  switch (readyMask)
5205  {
5206  case RAVAGERS_3 | RAVAGERS_4:
5207  if (urand(0, 1))
5208  return RAVAGERS_3;
5209  else
5210  return RAVAGERS_4;
5211  case RAVAGERS_3:
5212  return RAVAGERS_3;
5213  case RAVAGERS_4:
5214  return RAVAGERS_4;
5215  default:
5216  return NONE;
5217  }
5218  }
5219 
5220  IllidariAttackGroup ChooseIllidariNotRavagers3or4(uint8 readyMask)
5221  {
5222  if (urand(0, 5) <= 2)
5223  {
5224  readyMask = readyMask & (RAVAGERS_1 | RAVAGERS_2);
5225  switch (readyMask)
5226  {
5227  case RAVAGERS_1 | RAVAGERS_2:
5228  if (urand(0, 1))
5229  return RAVAGERS_1;
5230  else
5231  return RAVAGERS_2;
5232  case RAVAGERS_1:
5233  return RAVAGERS_1;
5234  case RAVAGERS_2:
5235  return RAVAGERS_2;
5236  default:
5237  return NONE;
5238  }
5239  }
5240  else
5241  {
5242  readyMask = readyMask & (SHADOWHOOF_1 | SHADOWHOOF_2 | SHADOWHOOF_3);
5243  switch (readyMask)
5244  {
5245  case SHADOWHOOF_1 | SHADOWHOOF_2 | SHADOWHOOF_3:
5246  if (!urand(0, 2))
5247  return SHADOWHOOF_1;
5248  else if (urand(0, 1))
5249  return SHADOWHOOF_2;
5250  else
5251  return SHADOWHOOF_3;
5252  case SHADOWHOOF_1 | SHADOWHOOF_2:
5253  return SHADOWHOOF_2;
5254  case SHADOWHOOF_1 | SHADOWHOOF_3:
5255  return SHADOWHOOF_1;
5256  case SHADOWHOOF_2 | SHADOWHOOF_3:
5257  return SHADOWHOOF_3;
5258  case SHADOWHOOF_1:
5259  return SHADOWHOOF_1;
5260  case SHADOWHOOF_2:
5261  return SHADOWHOOF_2;
5262  case SHADOWHOOF_3:
5263  return SHADOWHOOF_3;
5264  default:
5265  return NONE;
5266  }
5267  }
5268  }
5269 
5270  void UpdateAI(const uint32 diff) override
5271  {
5272  if (m_fIllidariAttackTimer < diff)
5273  {
5274  SendIllidariAttack();
5275 
5276  m_fIllidariAttackTimer = ILLIDARI_ATTACK_INTERVAL;
5277  }
5278  else
5279  m_fIllidariAttackTimer -= diff;
5280 
5281  if (m_fAldorScryerReinforceTimer < diff)
5282  {
5283  ReinforceAldorScryerFrontline();
5284 
5285  m_fAldorScryerReinforceTimer = REINFORCE_INTERVAL;
5286  }
5287  else
5288  m_fAldorScryerReinforceTimer -= diff;
5289  }
5290 };

5297 struct TagGreaterFelfireDiemetradon : public SpellScript, public AuraScript
5298 {
5299  SpellCastResult OnCheckCast(Spell* spell, bool strict) const override
5300  {
5301  Unit* target = spell->m_targets.getUnitTarget();
5302  if (!target || !target->IsCreature() || static_cast<Creature*>(target)->HasBeenHitBySpell(spell->m_spellInfo->Id))
5303  return SPELL_FAILED_BAD_TARGETS;
5304  return SPELL_CAST_OK;
5305  }

5310  if (target)
5311  static_cast<Creature*>(target)->RegisterHitBySpell(spell->m_spellInfo->Id);
5312  }
5313

5315  {
5316  if (apply)
5317  static_cast<Creature*>(aura->GetTarget())->UnregisterHitBySpell(aura->GetSpellProto()->Id);
5318  }
